          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1702388409704-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1702388409704-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine <strong>half</strong> your <strong>dried thyme</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> in a bowl<strong> </strong>with the <strong>cubed potatoes</strong>, <strong>lemon zest</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– these are your<strong> marinated potatoes</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>marinated potatoes</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) and put the tray[s] in the oven for 25 min or until golden and crisp – these are your <strong>smoky, lemon & thyme potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
