      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are nearly ready, put the tray[s] with the goats' cheese montadito in the oven and cook for 2-3 min or until slightly melted</p><p>Once slightly melted, remove the tray[s] from the oven and top with your <strong>sliced prosciutto</strong> – these are your <strong>prosciutto, truffled honey & goats' cheese montadito</strong></p>",
