      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>prosciutto, truffled honey & goats' cheese montadito </strong>with the<strong> dressed salad </strong>and<strong> smoky, lemon & thyme potatoes </strong>to the side</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
